			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Animated Loading Screen</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 10:39, 19 May 2015 by <a href="/User:Sychris" title="User:Sychris" class="mw-userlink">Sychris</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:Sychris&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Sychris (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/Sychris" title="Special:Contributions/Sychris">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
