<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="#So_how_did_I_use_that_to_get_a_loading_screen.3F"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">So how did I use that to get a loading screen?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="#11_Short_Steps_to_Create_an_Animated_Loading_Screen"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">11 Short Steps to Create an Animated Loading Screen</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="#Wrap-Up"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Wrap-Up</span></a></li>
</ul>
